      "author": "ludovicchabant",
      "description": "**New Features**\r\n\r\n- The state of files is now remembered on exit and saved to a file on disk. The files will be re-opened in their remembered state during the next session.\r\n\r\n**Bug Fixes**\r\n\r\n- Files open in multiple tabs should now be better handled. The remembered state from the last time that file was closed will be restored, unless no remembered state exists in which case it restores the state of the first other tab showing that file.\r\n",
      "draft": false,
      "name": "1.1.0",
      "prerelease": false,
      "publishedAt": "2023-09-21T06:21:18Z",
      "tag": "1.1.0"
    },
